  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd4\u0d82\u0da0\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd4 \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A dirty egg attack on Pohottu Panchi MP",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Pohottu councilor Mrs. Surangi Renuka Samaratunga, who was attacked by a group of Anuradhapura Municipal Council employees, was rescued by the police.",
        "The councilor who faced this incident says that yesterday (26) she attacked the Municipal Commissioner Ruwan Wijesinghe with a pair of shoes and insulted him in the finance committee chaired by the Mayor HP Somadasa.",
        "After that incident, the councilor came to the city council this morning (27th) and when she was waiting in the office of the councilors there, a large group of officials and employees of the city council came to the place and informed her to leave the city council.",
        "But as she sat down in the office of the MPs and did not respond, the workers took her to the lower floor along with the chair she was sitting on.",
        "A very hot situation arose there. The employees started protesting by displaying various posters accusing her in front of the entrance to the municipal council. The workers here told the councilor to apologize to the municipal commissioner for attacking the municipal commissioner with cursed shoes and she apologized to the commissioner who came to the place.",
        "Later, the employees took the councilwoman to the back of the city council and loaded her on a garbage trolley and tried to take her out of the city council, but due to another group of people protesting, the effort failed.",
        "Then the municipal councilor was taken back to the main entrance of the municipal council and taken out of the municipal council amid loud noises and water attacks.",
        "The incident was resolved after the MP was taken away from the municipal council premises in a police cab under the protection of a group of women police officers of the Anuradhapura Police."
      ],
